####Diapausing Pupal Weight Data Fall 2016
```{r}
#assign csv to "data"
data <- read.table("CompBio_Data_Set.csv", header=TRUE, sep=",", stringsAsFactors = F)
#Data for first 6 individuals 
head(data)
#Data for last 6 individuals 
tail(data)
#Looks at the structure of the data set. Here: 29 obs. 14 variables 
str(data)
#Summarizes the data set with major values, characters, etc. 
summary(data)

#To make sure there are only 3 photoperiods
table(data$Photoperiod)

#To make sure there are only 3 temperatures
table(data$Temperature)

#To make sure there are only 5 populations
table(data$Population)

```
